            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Hd1e108">Rubrica 4</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De paucitatis acceptabilitate et reprobatione multitudinis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>
      ¶ De paucitatis acceptabilitate
      <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>et reprobatione multitudinis.
      <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>Rubrica. 4
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e123">
               <lb ed="#V" n="72"/> <ref>ARisto. Ethicorum. li. 5. c.
      <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e129">Multis esse ami
        <lb ed="#V" n="74" break="no"/>cum secundum perfectam amicitiam non
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>contingit: quemadmodum neque ama
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>re multas simul. Multas simul eidem pla
        <lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>cere valde non facile.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e141"> <ref>/ Li. 9. c. 11.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e143">Diffici
        <lb ed="#V" n="78" break="no"/>le fit et congaudere et condolere familiari
        <lb ed="#V" n="79" break="no"/>ter multis. Non contingere videbitur mul
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>tis esse amicum valde: propter quod neque amare
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>plures.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e156"> <ref>/ Idem politicorum. li. 2. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e158">Multi ser
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>uientes quoniamque deterius seruiunt paucioribus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e164">
               <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>
                <ref>/ 8. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e168">Unum opus ab vno optime perficitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e172">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>
                <ref>/ 9. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e176">Non est facile prospicere multa vnum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e180">
               <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>
                <ref>/ Li. 4. c. 12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e184">Melius vnumquoque opus sor
        <lb ed="#V" n="86" break="no"/>titur cura circa vnum intenta quam circa mul
        <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>ta.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e192"> <ref>/ Li. 7. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e194">Difficile forte aut impossibi
        <lb ed="#V" n="88" break="no"/>le bene legibus regi eam ciuitatem que val
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>de multorum hominum est. Ualde exce
        <lb ed="#V" n="90" break="no"/>dens numerus non potest participare ordinem. <!--212.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="87-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e211">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
               <ref>/ Idem retho. li. 3. et fi. c. 14.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e215">Quanto fuerit
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>maior populus: tanto remotior intellectus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e222">
               <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>
                <ref>/ Idem topicorum: lib. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e226">Uerisimile est in
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>multis magis quam in paucis peccatum fieri.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e232">
               <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>
                <ref>¶ Tullius tusculanarum quoionum: li. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e236">Pau
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>ca ipsa sepe multum prosunt et ferunt fructus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e242">
               <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>
               <ref>¶ Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum: li. i. c. 2.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e246">Distrahit librorum multitudo: itaque cum le
        <lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>gere non possis quantum habueris satis est
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>habere quantum legas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e256"> <ref>/ Li. 6. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e258">Lectio
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>crebra prodest vana delectat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e264"> <ref>/ Idem de tram
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>quillitate animi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e266">Onerat discentem turba li
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>brorum: non instituit multoque satius est pau
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>cis te auctoribus tradere quam errare per mul
        <lb ed="#V" n="15" break="no"/>tos.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e278"> <ref>/ Idem de beneficiis: li. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e280">Solet plus
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>prodesse si pauca precepta sapientie teneas:
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>sed illa in promptu et in vsu tibi sint: quam si
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>multa quidem didiceris: sed illa non habe
        <lb ed="#V" n="19" break="no"/>as ad manum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e293"> <ref>/ Idem de consolatione ad
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>elbiamimatrem:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e295">Cupiditati nihil satis est:
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>nature satis est etiam parum. Necessariis rebus
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>exilia sufficiunt: superuacuis non regna</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e305">
               <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>
                <ref>/ Idem de beata vita.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e309">Argumentum pessi
        <lb ed="#V" n="24" break="no"/>mi turba est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e315">
               <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>
                <ref>¶ Lex cod. ti. de veteri iure enucleando: li. 2.
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>§. sed et si quid.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e319">Multo melius est pauca
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>idonee effundere quam multis inutilibus ho
        <lb ed="#V" n="28" break="no"/>mines pregrauari.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e329"> <ref>/ Lex auten. ti. de referen
        <lb ed="#V" n="29" break="no"/>dariis sacri palatii ad finem.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e331">Multitudo ho
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>minum numerosa nihil habet honestum:
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>quoniam paucis ex multis que secundum virtu
        <lb ed="#V" n="32" break="no"/>tem est vita saluatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e343">
               <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>
                <ref>¶ Uegetius de re militari: li. i. ti. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e347">In certa
        <lb ed="#V" n="34" break="no"/>mine bellorum exercitata paucitas ad victo
        <lb ed="#V" n="35" break="no"/>riam est promptior: rudis et indomita mul
        <lb ed="#V" n="36" break="no"/>titudo exposita semper ad cedem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e357"> <ref>/ Lib. 3.
        <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>titu. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e359">Pluribus casibus subiacet amplior
        <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>multitudo.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e368">
               <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>
               <ref>¶ Marcialis cocus vel vndique suscepto. c. 2.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e372">Predicat hermagoras non omnibus esse placendum.
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>Elige de multis regule cui placeas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e380">
               <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>
                <ref>¶ Boetius de consolatione: li. 2. c. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e384">Pau
        <lb ed="#V" n="43" break="no"/>cis minimisque natura contenta est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e390">
               <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>
               <ref>¶ Cassiodorus epistolarum: li. 7. e. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e394">Dum
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>tempus potantis prolixum queritur culpa <!--212.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>rum opprobria non vitantur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e406"> <ref>/ 9. e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e408">A pau
        <lb ed="#V" n="47" break="no"/>cis accipit qui nimium querit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e414">
               <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>
                <ref>¶ Gregorius in pastorali. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e418">Impar quisque
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>inuenitur ad singula dum confusa mente di
        <lb ed="#V" n="50" break="no"/>uiditur ad multa. Nequaquam plene vniuscu
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>iusque operis ratio colligitur dum mens per
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>diuersa partitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e430">
               <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>
               <ref>¶ Montenarius in luna cleri. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e434">Mens va
        <lb ed="#V" n="54" break="no"/>riis hebetatur dedita curis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e441"> <ref>/ c. 93.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e443">Plura
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>petit vicium: paucis natura fouetur:</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e449">
               <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>
                <ref>¶ Prouerb. metricur. extraoro vel vag.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e453">Pluri
        <lb ed="#V" n="57" break="no"/>bus intentus minor est ad singula sensus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>Qui binos lepores vna sectabitur hora:
        <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>Uno quandoque: quandoque carebit vtroque.
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>Segnius expediut commissa negocia plures.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-d1e465">
               <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>
               <ref>¶ Prouerb. vulg.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69585-Qd1e469">Chi doe leuore caza luna
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>perda elaltra lassa.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
